  {
    "uuid": "126e85c1-f453-53da-b460-efa60822292d",
    "entry": "混合器",
    "reading": {
      "primary": "こんごうき",
      "alternatives": [],
      "is_heteronym": false
    },
    "grammar": {
      "pos": [
        "名詞"
      ],
      "ctype": null,
      "inflections": null
    },
    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "(frequency) mixer",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "無線機の回路設計において、周波数を変換するための混合器は欠かせない部品だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "この高周波混合器は、ノイズを抑えつつ信号を効率よく変換できる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "混合器の性能が、受信機の感度に直接影響を与えることがある。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "gloss": "mixer (ingredients, etc.)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "ケーキの生地を滑らかにするために、電動の混合器を使って手早く混ぜる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "厨房には、大量の野菜を瞬時に細かくできるプロ仕様の混合器が備わっている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "新しい混合器を導入したおかげで、ソースの仕上がりが一段と良くなった。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      }
